The answer of the doge and barons was simple and magnanimous . 
In the cause of honor and justice , they said , we despise the usurper of Greece , his threats , and his offers . 
Let that brother confess his guilt , and implore forgiveness , and we ourselves will intercede , that he may be permitted to live in affluence and security . 
But let him not insult us by a second message our reply will be made in arms , in the palace of Constantinople . 
