The style of their ambassadors to Conrad the Third and Frederic the First is a mixture of flattery and pride , the tradition and the ignorance of their own history . 
After some complaint of his silence and neglect , they exhort the former of these princes to pass the Alps , and assume from their hands the Imperial crown . 
The pope and the Sicilian are united in an impious league to oppose our liberty and your coronation . 
With the blessing of God , our zeal and courage has hitherto defeated their attempts . 
